Author: Jade222Gem
Text: It seems to temporarily speed it up and jump start it.  I never put on any weight when I have an occasional cheat meal, and I seem to lose weight for a couple of days afterwards, too. I don't know if that's the same for everyone.

Author: LolitaJane
Text: You canâ€™t trick your body no matter when or how much you eat.  The only increase in metabolism that results from a cheat meal/day is from the thermic effect of the food you ate, and is pretty much negligible for any sort of weight loss calculation.
